nodes.text: Aq Vetina was a settlement inhabited by a number of humans. During the Clone Wars, the Confederacy of Independent Systems attacked the settlement, killing the population. The Mandalorians of Death Watch intervened in the attack, fighting back against the Separatist droid forces. The young human Din Djarin was rescued by one Mandalorian warrior, and was raised as a foundling in the Mandalorian creed.
